              <h3 class="card-title">If you are a fan you can</h3>
                 <ul>
                     <li> Create amazing circuits and share on the platform</li>
                     <li> Find and report bugs. Become a bug hunter</li>
                     <li> Introduce the platform to your buddies</li>

                 </ul>
                 <h4>If you are a developer you can</h4>
                 <ul>
                     <li>Contribute to the open source project</li>
                     <li>Add new features and fix bugs</li>
                 </ul>
                 <h4>If you are an company/organization you can</h4>
                 <ul>
                     <li>Become a CircuitVerse Partner (see Patreon)</li>
                     <li>Contact support for more details</li>
                 </ul>
            </div>
           <div class="col-6">

             <h4>If you are a teacher you can</h4>
               <ul>
                 <li> Introduce the platform to your students</li>
                 <li> Promote the platform within your circles</li>
                 <li> Create exciting educational content using CircuitVerse </li>
               </ul>
             <h4>If you have money to spare you can</h4>
               <ul>
                 <li> Become a patreon (recurring pledge)</li>
                 <li> Donate via PayPal (one time)</li>
               </ul>
